  "title": "Cybersecurity Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Computer and Network Security Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a<strong> Cybersecurity Project Manager</strong> to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead, plan, and execute <strong>cybersecurity projects—including VAPT, Asset Discovery, Risk Assessment, GRC, and related initiatives</strong>—through all phases from initiation to closure.</li><li>Develop comprehensive project plans, including timelines, milestones, and resource allocation, to ensure delivery on schedule and within scope.</li><li>Monitor project progress, identify risks, track issues and dependencies, and escalate matters as needed.</li><li>Prepare and deliver regular project status updates, reports, and dashboards to stakeholders and management.</li><li>Conduct and contribute to IT risk assessment activities, including risk identification, impact and likelihood evaluation, and risk mitigation planning.</li><li>Oversee and coordinate governance and compliance efforts aligned with<strong> standards and regulations such as ISO 27001, IM8, PDPA, </strong>or other industry frameworks.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma from Computer Science / Cybersecurity related discipline of study</li><li><strong>3 years of working experience</strong> in project management involving <strong>IT risk, governance, or compliance</strong></li><li>Familiarity with <strong>GRC frameworks and standards</strong> such as ISO 27001, NIST, COBIT, PDPA, or equivalent  is advantageous.</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em><br /></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em></p><p><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em></p><p><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
